A member of the [[Brotherhood of the Cloak]] in [[Mulmaster]], Malkyn abandoned her city and was chosen to join the First Lord's court.

''Circa'' [[1486 DR]], she attended the First Lord's [[Midsummer Masquerade]] ball.{{Cite adventurers league/Hillsfar Reclaimed|12}}

During the ball, Torin started a speech and an [[elf]] assassin tried to kill the First Lord but hit only [[Thessaly Malaeda]]. Malkyn quickly reached Torin and the two disappeared thanks to an ''[[invisibility]]'' [[spell]] and she took the Lord to a safe place.{{Cite adventurers league/Hillsfar Reclaimed|18}}

